Projects.project_summary: Elix introduces a new generation of decentralized exchanges (DEX) based on Fuel, the first modular execution layer powered by the innovative FuelVM. By leveraging a new approach to previous AMM designs alongside Fuel’s parallel transaction execution, Elix will provide high capital efficiency, flexible pools, automated liquidity and transactions at lightning speed and maximum security.
Fluid Protocol is building USDF, the native decentralized stablecoin for the Fuel Ecosystem
Acumen is a lending protocol building on Fuel that provides sustainable yields for users whilst empowering emerging economies.
Swaylend is a Compound inspired lending protocol building on Fuel.
Microchain systems is a UniV2 Inspired Dex launching on Fuel.
Thunder is a best in class NFT marketplace building on Fuel, allowing for bulk transaction execution, and taking full advantage of the Fuel stack.

PlayEstates’ mission is to make real asset investment accessible and fun. PlayEstates fractionalizes and tokenizes real-world property assets into the forms of non-fungible-tokens (NFTs). This means that our NFTs have real world value.
Redstone is a protocol offering oracles that provide frequently updated, reliable and diverse data for your dApp and smart contracts.
The next generation name service running on Fuel
Smartmoney is  truly decentralized Lending and Burrowing protocol, backed by collateral and therefore offering greater flexibility to end users.
Poolshark is a directional AMM where users can profit from volatility with less maintenance. Traders can now be LPs too.
Yama is a novel omnichain stablecoin that facilitates extremely high leverage
